snippet.textDisplay: My favorite song, Laadki from Coke Studio, always reminds me of my father. It speaks to the bond we share, and I truly believe he would never have left me. No matter what happens, he holds my hand when the whole world falls apart. He’s always been my rock in a hard place, my shoulder to lean on, and I’ve weathered the storm together with him through thick and thin. 💖🎶
